## Customer Services APIs

<!-- type: row -->

<!-- type: card
title: Create Customer Profile
description: Register a customer in the uCom system
link: ../api/?type=post&path=/v1/customers
-->

<!-- type: card
title: Delete Customer Profile </h3>
description: Delete a customer profile from uCom system by providing the fdCustomerId
link: ../api/?type=delete&path=/v1/customers/{fdCustomerId}
-->

<!-- type: row -->

<!-- type: card
title: Get Customer Profile by externalId </h3>
description: Fetch the details of a customer providing the externalId
link: ../api/?type=get&path=/v1/customers
-->

<!-- type: card
title: Get Customer Profile by fdCustomerId </h3>
description: Fetch the details of a customer providing the fdCustomerId
link: ..api/?type=get&path=/v1/customers/{fdCustomerId}
-->